  "text": "PAI-1 antigen levels are strongly associated with visceral adiposity in the general population [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and are reported to be higher in HIV-infected individuals compared to controls in association with increased visceral adiposity [CITATION_3] and protease inhibitor use [CITATION_4] .",
